WEBVTT

00:09:55.861 --> 00:10:01.433
one child is suffering, and in the other,
that same child is not suffering.

00:10:01.457 --> 00:10:03.513
Control for everything else.

00:10:03.537 --> 00:10:07.801
And it feels like it's not a stretch
to say, as a fact,

00:10:07.825 --> 00:10:11.183
that that universe where the child
is not suffering is better.

00:10:11.207 --> 00:10:16.175
SH: Yeah. So as long as you can give me
the spectrum of better and worse,

00:10:16.199 --> 00:10:17.474
that's all I need.

00:10:17.498 --> 00:10:22.491
And there are several double standards
here that people observe by default,

00:10:22.515 --> 00:10:27.408
which are the source of what I would argue
is our confusion about morality.

00:10:27.432 --> 00:10:29.876
So one double standard

00:10:29.900 --> 00:10:32.185
is that even the most
hard-headed scientist